<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>E-commerce Redesign - Annie Sommer</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@picocss/pico@2/css/pico.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --text-color: #34495e;
            --light-gray: #ecf0f1;
            --border-color: #bdc3c7;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-color);
            max-width: 42rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
        
        header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .back-link {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        
        .project-header {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .project-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        
        .project-meta {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        .project-summary {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #5d6d7e;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
        }
        
        .content-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .content-section h3 {
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }
        
        .image-placeholder {
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
            border: 2px dashed var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
        
        .navigation {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        
        .nav-link {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        footer {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            text-align: center;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to portfolio</a>
        
        <div class="project-header">
            <h1>E-commerce Platform Redesign</h1>
            
            <div class="project-meta">
                <span><strong>Role:</strong> UX/UI Designer</span>
                <span><strong>Duration:</strong> 3 months</span>
                <span><strong>Year:</strong> 2024</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="project-summary">
                A comprehensive redesign of an e-commerce platform focused on improving user experience, increasing conversion rates, and modernizing the visual design. This project involved extensive user research, prototyping, and iterative testing.
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>The Challenge</h2>
            <p>The existing e-commerce platform was experiencing declining user engagement and poor conversion rates. Users were abandoning their shopping carts at a rate of 70%, and customer feedback indicated frustration with the complex checkout process and outdated interface.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h3>Key Problems Identified</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Complicated navigation structure</li>
                    <li>Lengthy checkout process with 7 steps</li>
                    <li>Poor mobile responsiveness</li>
                    <li>Lack of trust indicators</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Research & Discovery</h2>
            <p>I conducted user interviews with 15 existing customers and performed a comprehensive audit of the current platform. The research revealed that users valued simplicity, security, and speed above flashy design elements.</p>
            
            <div class="image-placeholder">
                [User Journey Map Image]
            </div>
            
            <h3>Key Insights</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Users wanted to complete purchases in under 3 minutes</li>
                <li>Mobile traffic accounted for 65% of visits but only 30% of conversions</li>
                <li>Trust badges and security indicators were crucial for purchase decisions</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Design Solution</h2>
            <p>Based on the research findings, I redesigned the platform with a focus on simplification and user-centered design principles.</p>
            
            <div class="image-placeholder">
                [Before/After Comparison Images]
            </div>
            
            <h3>Key Improvements</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Streamlined checkout:</strong> Reduced from 7 steps to 3</li>
                <li><strong>Mobile-first design:</strong> Optimized for touch interactions</li>
                <li><strong>Enhanced trust signals:</strong> Added security badges and customer reviews</li>
                <li><strong>Improved navigation:</strong> Simplified menu structure and search functionality</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Results</h2>
            <p>The redesigned platform launched after 3 months of development and testing. The results exceeded our initial goals and demonstrated the impact of user-centered design.</p>
            
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">40%</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Increase in conversions</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">65%</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Reduction in cart abandonment</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">2.3x</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Mobile conversion improvement</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">4.5/5</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">User satisfaction score</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Lessons Learned</h2>
            <p>This project reinforced the importance of user research in driving design decisions. The most impactful changes weren't always the most visually dramatic—sometimes simplifying existing flows had the greatest effect on user experience.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>Key Takeaway:</strong> Success in e-commerce design comes from removing friction, not adding features.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <nav class="navigation">
        <a href="/" class="nav-link">← Back to portfolio</a>
